e. Fire tortillas, great baked goods. The only shitty thing is the line but what are you gonna do it's great food. Also their egg burritos aren't for me, but I'm just not an egg guy.\n\nI'd honestly argue you should just get the bean and cheese burrito because the tortillas are the star of the show.","google_maps_url":"https://maps.app.goo.gl/AE9rC1x3Ldo6s5Q1A","place_id":null,"lat":40.6702347,"lng":-73.9789938}],"osmPois":[],"osmTotal":1},{"restaurants":[{"slug":"sottovoce","title":"SottoVoce","stars":5,"vibe":"sit-down","status":"reviewed","date":"2026-04-19","review":"Super family style vibe, the people there really care more about the food they serve than appearing any sort of way (complimentary). The sauces we got had clear depth and thought put into what the experience of eating the pasta would be like. The vodka sauce I had was creamy and smokey, but very subtle without completely losing any complexity. I was really impressed, I'm a huge Italian hater, so good job SottoVoce.","google_maps_url":"https://maps.app.goo.gl/CzfU23v3Dz9xPCQn8","place_id":null,"lat":40.6699181,"lng":-73.9787674}],"osmPois":[{"name":"Juice Press","lat":40.6703017,"lng":-73.9785398}],"osmTotal":1},{"restaurants":[],"osmPois":[],"osmTotal":0}],[{"restaurants":[],"osmPois":[],"osmTotal":0},{"restaurants":[],"osmPois":[{"name":"Bagel World","lat":40.6720373,"lng":-73.9837179},{"name":"Park Slope Ale House","lat":40.6706029,"lng":-73.9819872},{"name":"Joe's Pizza","lat":40.6718133,"lng":-73.9839044},{"name":"L'Albero Dei Gelati","lat":40.671995,"lng":-73.9837531},{"name":"Café Martin","lat":40.6716935,"lng":-73.9840041},{"name":"Terre","lat":40.6719617,"lng":-73.9837809},{"name":"Flavored Flames","lat":40.6717517,"lng":-73.9839556}],"osmTotal":7},{"restaurants":[],"osmPois":[{"name":"Bobo's Smoothies","lat":40.6695964,"lng":-73.9795166},{"name":"Just Salad","lat":40.6694841,"lng":-73.9796096},{"name":"Poetica Coffee","lat":40.6696923,"lng":-73.9794371},{"name":"One More Charm","lat":40.669