Purity","stars":5,"vibe":"casual-sit-down","status":"reviewed","date":"2026-04-19","review":"The food here is fine, they make their own sauces and such in house but it's nothing that'll blow your mind.\n\nLittle Purity gets 5 stars because it is one of the friendliest, most welcoming places you'll go to in the city. They've been there for a couple decades, and the brother and sister duo who run it are really in it for the love of the game. I encourage whoever is reading this, to take some time, get a coffee, and meet the fun and kind owners of this place.","google_maps_url":"https://maps.app.goo.gl/F7EaEVjgLSXVbkXz9","place_id":null,"lat":40.6652699,"lng":-73.9831689},{"slug":"norm-s-pizza","title":"Norm's Pizza","stars":1,"vibe":"grab-and-go","status":"reviewed","date":"2026-04-19","review":"Eh. Probably some of the worst pizza I've had in NY, the place barely has a menu, and it closes early so it really has nothing going for it. There's a Joe's around the corner and a Smiling Pizza up north a couple blocks that at least make a decent slice.","google_maps_url":"https://maps.app.goo.gl/9MNnFtT2VDfa8SfD9","place_id":null,"lat":40.6653261,"lng":-73.9831292}],"osmPois":[],"osmTotal":3},{"restaurants":[{"slug":"brookvin","title":"Brookvin","stars":4,"vibe":"bar","status":"reviewed","date":"2026-04-19","review":"I'm not a wine guy but I liked what I had here, the vibe was really nice but this place really shines with the excellent staff. Everyone there is so friendly, they'll remember your name, it's a great place to go to as a local and get to know the staff.","google_maps_url":"https://maps.app.goo.gl/dcDrhhH4ynKweJXDA","place_id":null,"lat":40.6653374,"lng":-73.9826828}],"osmPois":[{"name":"Pasta Louise","lat":40.6642108,"lng":-73.9807113},{"name":"Osaki Sushi","lat":40.664375,"lng":-73.9805542}],"osmTotal":2},{"restaurants":[],"osmPois":[{"name":"Ottava","lat":40.663955,"lng":-73.9805265},{"name":"Saint Eves","lat":40.6638376,"lng":-73.9802832}],"osmTotal":2}],[{"res